Comment
Billed as "A Swell Dance Concert"
Sons Of Champlin were on the bill to open but did not play due to the death of the lead singer's father. New Riders Of The Purple Sage opened instead.

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals
